# Great Leap App - Setup & Testing Checklist
# ============================================

## ✅ Before You Start
- [ ] npm installed (check: npm --version)
- [ ] Node.js installed (check: node --version)
- [ ] You're in project directory: /Users/user1/Desktop/great-leap-app01

## ✅ Installation
- [ ] Run: npm install
- [ ] Wait for completion (2-3 minutes)
- [ ] Check for errors

## ✅ Development Server
- [ ] Run: npm run dev
- [ ] Should show: "Local: http://localhost:5173/"
- [ ] Server stays running (don't close terminal)

## ✅ Testing - Landing Page
- [ ] Open browser to: http://localhost:5173/
- [ ] Page loads without white screen
- [ ] Logo "⚡ Great Leap" visible in top left
- [ ] Navigation menu visible (Features, How It Works, Benefits)
- [ ] Hero section shows headline
- [ ] All 9 sections visible when scrolling
- [ ] "Get Started" button visible
- [ ] "Login" button visible in header
- [ ] Smooth scroll animations work
- [ ] Icons render correctly (checkmarks, lightning, etc.)
- [ ] Open DevTools (F12) - Console clean (no errors)

## ✅ Testing - Signup Flow
- [ ] Click "Get Started" button
- [ ] Navigate to http://localhost:5173/signup
- [ ] Page loads (Step 1: Company Details)
- [ ] Can type in Company Name field
- [ ] Can type in Company Email field
- [ ] Can type in Subdomain field
- [ ] "Check Availability" button works
- [ ] "Next" button active
- [ ] Error messages appear for empty fields
- [ ] Fill Step 1 completely
- [ ] Click Next → Go to Step 2
- [ ] Fill admin name
- [ ] Fill admin email
- [ ] Fill password (8+ chars)
- [ ] Fill confirm password
- [ ] Errors show if passwords don't match
- [ ] Click Next → Go to Step 3
- [ ] See 3 plan options (Free, Starter, Pro)
- [ ] Can select each plan
- [ ] Click Next → Go to Step 4
- [ ] See confirmation message
- [ ] See company details summary
- [ ] Check localStorage has token:
    - Open DevTools (F12)
    - Go to Application > LocalStorage
    - Verify: auth_token, user, tenant_id exist

## ✅ Testing - Login Page
- [ ] Visit: http://localhost:5173/login
